Class Donut

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.kordamp.jsilhouette.javafx.AbstractSilhouette
      • org.kordamp.jsilhouette.javafx.AbstractCenteredSilhouette
        • org.kordamp.jsilhouette.javafx.Donut
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    CenteredSilhouette, Silhouette

    public class Donut
extends AbstractCenteredSilhouette

    Donut

    Defines a donut shape based on circles or regular polygons.

    Constraints

    1. ir <= or

    2. ir > 0 && or > 0

    3. sides == 0 || sides > 2

    Style Classes

    1. silhouette

    2. silhouette-donut

    Author:
    Andres Almiray
